ITEM.DESCRIPT: Convert FM Data to object attributes

ITEM.SOURCE:
DATA s_func LIKE LINE OF functions. DATA s_f_txt LIKE LINE OF s_func-texts. DATA s_param LIKE LINE OF s_func-parameters. DATA s_excep LIKE LINE OF s_func-exceptions. FIELD-SYMBOLS: LIKE LINE OF fm_data-function_texts, LIKE LINE OF fm_data-functions, LIKE LINE OF -import_p, LIKE LINE OF -changing_p, LIKE LINE OF -export_p,

LIKE LINE OF s_func-parameters, LIKE LINE OF fm_data-param_texts, LIKE LINE OF -exceptions, LIKE LINE OF -tables. a0_maindata = fm_data-header. textspool = fm_data-textspool. dynpros = fm_data-dynpros. menupainter = fm_data-menupainter. includes = fm_data-includes. LOOP AT fm_data-functions ASSIGNING . CLEAR s_func. MOVE-CORRESPONDING -header TO s_func. s_func-source-_ = -source. LOOP AT fm_data-function_texts ASSIGNING WHERE funcname = s_func-name. CLEAR s_f_txt. s_f_txt-langu = -spras. s_f_txt-short_txt = -stext. INSERT s_f_txt INTO TABLE s_func-texts. ENDLOOP. LOOP AT -import_p ASSIGNING . CLEAR s_param. s_param-hdr = . s_param-kind = parameter_kinds-importing. INSERT s_param INTO TABLE s_func-parameters. ENDLOOP. LOOP AT -changing_p ASSIGNING . CLEAR s_param. s_param-hdr = . s_param-kind = parameter_kinds-changing. INSERT s_param INTO TABLE s_func-parameters. ENDLOOP. LOOP AT -export_p ASSIGNING . CLEAR s_param. MOVE-CORRESPONDING TO s_param-hdr. s_param-kind = parameter_kinds-exporting. INSERT s_param INTO TABLE s_func-parameters. ENDLOOP. LOOP AT -tables ASSIGNING . CLEAR s_param. MOVE-CORRESPONDING TO s_param-hdr. s_param-dbfield = -dbstruct. s_param-kind = parameter_kinds-table. INSERT s_param INTO TABLE s_func-parameters. ENDLOOP. LOOP AT s_func-parameters ASSIGNING

. LOOP AT fm_data-param_texts ASSIGNING WHERE funcname = s_func-name AND parameter =

-parameter AND kind = 'P'. CLEAR s_f_txt. s_f_txt-langu = -spras. s_f_txt-short_txt = -stext. INSERT s_f_txt INTO TABLE

-texts. ENDLOOP. ENDLOOP. LOOP AT -exceptions ASSIGNING . CLEAR s_excep. s_excep-hdr = . LOOP AT fm_data-param_texts ASSIGNING WHERE funcname = s_func-name AND parameter = -exception AND kind = 'X'. CLEAR s_f_txt. s_f_txt-langu = -spras. s_f_txt-short_txt = -stext. INSERT s_f_txt INTO TABLE s_excep-texts. ENDLOOP. INSERT s_excep INTO TABLE s_func-exceptions. ENDLOOP. INSERT s_func INTO TABLE functions. ENDLOOP.
